   "source": [
    "# SDE"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "636b9ace-f25b-4650-a9f0-641b0ef88518",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "`-` semi-linear SDEs of additive noise type\n",
    "\n",
    "$$dX(t)=F\\big(X(t)\\big)dt+\\Sigma dW(t):=\\big(AX(t)+N\\big(X(t)\\big)\\big)+\\Sigma dW(t)$$\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "eb9f4ad1-a5c2-4121-9436-2fceff895c17",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- $\\Sigma$: degenerate diffusion matrix \n",
    "- $F$: drift which satisfies a global one-side Lipschitz condition and is allowed to grow polynomially. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "c7db1465-fda2-4e99-bddc-6a3d37a49fe4",
